- Seasonal Garden Trio  CHF 92 per guest (wine pairings included; vegetarian; Available DecemberMarch). Charred leek tart, truffle risotto, and citrus pavlova matched with Swiss whites.

- Lakeview Signature Journey  CHF 118 per guest (wine pairings included; includes meat & seafood; Available FebruaryApril). Lake char crudo, veal tenderloin, and Swiss meringue finale with matching wines.
